Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,八雲…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,皇…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,卡連
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他真的…跟八雲交換身分了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,《緋紅結繫》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,倦怠感 losing yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,尚未找到建立關係的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有個麻煩的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,至死都在尋求某人的擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在得以喘息的混沌虛無之間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,以輸贏之間為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,注意別讓信任走向盡頭 務必小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see I'm always on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,今天仍拼命地聯繫著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你腦中那冷感的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,搖滾的日子未曾有過的浩劫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,光榮早已埋葬在某處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這一瞬間寂寞孤獨的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,與機關槍射出的子彈並列
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,射穿所有世間道理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,今天仍拼命地聯繫著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,與機關槍射出的子彈並列
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也仍在一起 清晰地聯繫著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你那腦中冷感的正義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(沉睡的思念)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,跟以往…不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這兩千年來 他都在這
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,卡連 有件事希望你協助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,為了消滅岐之門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,請你祝我們一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你在荒吐神時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,使用了紅色繫線跳躍時空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而接觸到兩千年前的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因此出現了維度糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,只要維度糾纏存在\N岐之門就不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再這樣下去 世界會毀滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 你得解開糾…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,解決不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,讓維度糾纏出現的人\N才能解開其糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都成功了 所以沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那為何不幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我解決不了 這就是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,卡連 當初你為了救愛麗絲\N才跳躍了時空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但 為何跳躍到兩千年前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,剛開始…我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,八雲皇 可能是紅色繫線的腦力者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 或許我是受到他的牽引吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,無預警地跳躍到兩千年前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我拼命地尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,能拯救兩千年後愛麗絲的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,能改變未來的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到的答案 就是成為八雲皇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,利用建國之父的身分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,應該能做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,做些什麼 那你做到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在遙遠的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一能拯救愛麗絲的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我自己與荒吐神連結
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,與所有系統的中樞荒吐神連結
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就能驅動歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就能拯救愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以荒吐神也是\N腦部組成的生物電腦囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,強制入侵我們腦部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也是你搞的鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,實際上 愛麗絲她…她無法復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我才不斷重複
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不斷重複…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,跳躍時空數次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,成為八雲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,維度糾纏也因此產生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我解開維度糾纏 也解決不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我會產生新的糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,卡連
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,卡連 有兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為何 你在這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你會在這…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我才想問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只要成為八雲 與荒吐神連結
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就有可能是拯救愛麗絲的唯一方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,跳躍時空 留在荒吐神裡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所有嘗試錯誤紀錄證明過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那我為何無法跳躍到兩千年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,為何我跳躍時空失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫過你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是你嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快交出所有的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,還有記憶… 我要吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,吸收了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂的與荒吐神連結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的記憶 都是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-什麼\N-難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你得到了荒吐神的情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不論你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,都不超過幾百…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,幾千…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,幾萬分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我以外的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我把相同情報給無數的我多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此 仍無法改變未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,無法救愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,觀察到這一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你只會白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,毫無所獲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,無限循環中的其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,別再妄想了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要救愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不管幾次 我都要救愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個 把紅色繫線交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你之所以跳躍時間失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是沒成功複製結人的超腦力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是哥哥的超腦力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也很難持續持有紅色繫線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才要一直複製
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你們抵抗也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我得到紅色繫線是必然的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,卡連
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,跳躍時空 會毀滅世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不論要用什麼手段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我都要再跳躍一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你不打算協助我們囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,新日向和月球 雖然有許多問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但世界毀滅的話就什麼都無法解決
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須創造出新的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,以這樣的歷史織羅而成的世界\N一點價值也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要改變過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這次一定要改變成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解你想救愛麗絲的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要妳的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,妳也不可能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,超腦力增強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,結人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你們能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,能放棄重要的事物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,通過許多艱難的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救這顆星球的紅色守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,兩位年輕的緋紅守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那岐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,結人皇上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,對上 那岐卡門上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 今天天氣好像不錯喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,成為怪伐軍 是你從小的願望嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要出去走走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我有想逛的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那岐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,結人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾想過 回到過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,救我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是結人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一定能救我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,妳很後悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧 重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果 當時那瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,妳注意到異狀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不會變成這副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你很後悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果 當時那瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那岐人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他被帶到醫院後 就沒跟我聯絡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你來找我 就不會演變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我…變得莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要我殺你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在耳邊響起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明不想戰鬥 這麼厭惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我很害怕 卻無法反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的確 後悔過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只要做出稍微不同的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,未來 或許就會不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,無論何時 我們只能做出一種選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,人活著 就得做出選擇往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,只能做出 當下最正確的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,結果你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,為了自已的私慾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而把重要事物一腳踢開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的思念不過就這點程度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 正因為有那岐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,別說得一副你很懂似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,正因為有那岐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是那岐 任何人發生什麼不測
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都不能閉上眼睛否認一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我的體悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是改變過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而是前往未來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我們非這麼做不可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你們的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,放棄過去 否認已發生的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是逃避問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何我都要救愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,卡連 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該有 愛麗絲期望你\N走向未來的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,快想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲並不希望\N毀滅世界來拯救自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你不准提愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的你應該能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你與荒吐神連結了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快想起愛麗絲的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就算知道什麼\N我也不會改變想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不管有多麼困難…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不會改變…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,紅色繫線交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,重 我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只要得到紅色繫線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你們就沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,重 跟卡連一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,從荒吐神的記憶裡尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,尋找愛麗絲真正的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她是位很好的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,能讓你如此思念她\N便是最好的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,卡連他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,總是幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可是今天 因此害他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那絕非一點皮肉傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是希望他別再幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,而是希望 他能更加善待自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我想一直跟他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我得更堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此 他還是會繼續保護妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我得更努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,為了讓卡連不再為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,而持續加油努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我希望 卡連能得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,卡連崔佛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的你過得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,覺得幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我 不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,結人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經複製你的紅色繫線了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣我就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,卡連…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲真正的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲妳等著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會停止的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這次一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一定能救愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,結人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只能這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,卡連
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,被追求的憧憬所困
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,揭開被阻擋的搖曳陽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a stranger in me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,從未見過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,自己能不再恐懼翱翔高空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm spreading my wings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,華麗舞步的鳥兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,仰望染紅的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,追過了強風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,景色蔓延在千變萬化的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在交錯的光芒中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,持續尋找明天的行徑方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's in your hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me now you're afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to waste
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不再畏懼何物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Into a brand new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.13,0:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,(消滅岐之門作戰)
